<h2>Intro</h2>
One of the great things about buying a fourty year old recreational
vehicle is the appliances which have sat outside, in the leaky vehicle,
for just as long. Also wasps.

<h2>Test Rig</h2>
<p>Sometimes a little preparation cuts down an awful lot of perspiration.</p>
<a data-flickr-embed="true"  href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/40925843@N03/25032616836/in/dateposted-public/" title="IMG_20160215_224757"><img src="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1545/25032616836_70eb7b95bc.jpg" width="500" height="375" alt="IMG_20160215_224757"></a>
<p>The Woodsman came with a large frame-mounted tank that is
in reasonable shape. But it is also winter outside. With a steak-saver
